<plot>Bill Harris, looking for border rustlers and working undercover, rides into town and makes friends with Fred Palmer, one of the rustlers. They both take an interest in Jane Wilson. When the boss of the rustlers learns of Bill's true identity, he uses their attraction to Jane to alienate the friends hoping Fred will kill Bill.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?079678</url></doc>
